snippet.title: FIRST LOOK - A Shenmue Story - NEW Shenmue Journey by George Kitchen! - Releasing December 15th!
snippet.description:
FIRST LOOK!

A NEW first person #Shenmue journey from George Kitchen!

Coming December 18th

Set at Xmas this is a short Shenmue adventure which has:

✅New Mini-Games

✅New Capsules

✅Chobu Chan

+ MORE!

It perfectly captures the Shenmue spirit!

Teaser below 👇
